  <prompt>Per FR-15: after 24-hr window passes, EITHER delete `spe-redis-dev-67e2xz` OR tag it with `decommission=YYYY-MM-DD`. Default to TAG (safer; allows reversal during a longer cooling-off if needed); delete only if explicit owner sign-off captured in cutover record.</prompt>
